| Layer    | Stack                        |
| -------- | ---------------------------- |
| Frontend | React + Tailwind/MUI         |
| Backend  | Node.js + Express            |
| Database | MongoDB + Mongoose           |
| Auth     | JWT + OAuth2.0 (Google, etc) |
| AI       | OpenAI API (GPT-4)           |
| Queueing | BullMQ + Redis               |
| Hosting  | Railway / Render (MVP)       |
